data.description: Open floor plan, modern kitchen, stainless refrigerator that conveys, two living spaces, or you can use the second living space as a master suite. Three bedrooms and two bathrooms upstairs, with the third bathroom downstairs, as well as the laundry room with a washer and dryer that convey. Enjoy the large backyard with an in-ground pool.
